==English==

===Noun===
'''perpetuity'''

# The quality or state of being [[perpetual]]; [[endless]] [[duration]]; [[uninterrupted]] [[existence]].
# Something that is perpetual.
# {{law}} A [[limitation]] intended to be [[unalterable]] and of [[indefinite]] [[duration]]; a [[disposition]] of [[property]] which attempts to make it [[inalienable]] beyond certain limits fixed or conceived as being fixed by the general law.

